  Locus:
    Page: 333
    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Nothing/Emptiness
---
When you have reduced yourself to nothing -- when your “self” has
disappeared -- when you have become nothing, then you are yourself God. The
man who is nothing knows God, for God is nothing. Nothing is everything.
